{"title": "Tackling climate change\u2019s impact on health tops insurer AIA\u2019s sustainability efforts", "tags": "business", "timestamp": "2024-08-10", "content": "SINGAPORE \u2013 Investing in the future of the planet also means investing in the health of its customers and the future of its business, says insurer AIA.\nThe major health insurance player views sustainability as a commitment that leads to benefits for people even as it helps to preserve the business of the company and ensure its longevity."}